
Screen sharing with chrome based WebRTC screen sharing
"This requires xdg-desktop-portal and one of its backends to be installed"
:

Added to .bashrc to get pipewire stuff OK

if [[ "$XDG_SESSION_DESKTOP" == sway ]]
then
    export XDG_CURRENT_DESKTOP=sway
    systemctl --user import-environment WAYLAND_DISPLAY XDG_CURRENT_DESKTOP
fi

In google-chrome
chrome://flags/#enable-webrtc-pipewire-capturer

